896
00:58:28,318 --> 00:58:29,919
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ji Ah, kau itu kenapa?</i></font>

897
00:58:32,188 --> 00:58:34,391
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya dia suka seperti itu.</font>

