00:58:46,603 --> 00:58:47,937
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagus sekali.</font>

901
00:58:48,772 --> 00:58:50,073
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang harus kita lakukan?/
Bong Hee.</font>

902
00:58:50,073 --> 00:58:51,141
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya?</font>

903
00:58:51,908 --> 00:58:52,909
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita memang sial.</font>

904
00:58:53,677 --> 00:58:54,911
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, gagal total.</font>

905
00:58:54,911 --> 00:58:55,912
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak tahu harus berkata apa.</font>

906
00:58:56,913 --> 00:58:58,348
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah kuduga ini bakal terjadi.</font>

907
00:58:58,948 --> 00:59:00,016
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak tahu.</font>

908
