<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana ini?</font>

909
00:59:03,353 --> 00:59:04,421
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa harus kita cat ulang lagi?</font>

910
00:59:04,821 --> 00:59:06,356
<font color=#FFFF00>Bong Hee, sebenarnya.../
